    "body": "Okay I can't replicate this anymore, so I don't think it's an actual issue, just user error.\n\nThe reason it was exiting early for me when testing with the actual code I wrote was because it was signaling another process with SIGINT, which doesn't work on Windows like it does in Unix. And I was also trying to do async code in the `process.on('exit', ...)` which isn't allowed as per Node docs.\n"
